Review Text: This is only restaurant in Gachibowli which serves Orginal Tanjvur Sambar. The taste has mesmerized me !!! It is really hard to get a pure south Indian restaurant, and finally I found a great one. Every recipe is tasteful and quality is awsome. Pls open ur branches in Nanakramguda and Gopanpalli. Our office canteen needs you guys. Pls come to our office ValueMomentum :)
